    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this car. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it that it\u2019s still in absolute showroom condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot! Not a single scratch or ding to be found. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, but it's time for someone else to enjoy how smoothly it handles. If you're looking for a ride that's basically brand new, this is your lucky day! Drop me a message if you want to come by and take a look!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
