    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional vehicle that presents in showroom condition. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory-original luster, completely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings. The alloy wheels are immaculate with no curb rash, wrapped in high-performance tires with ample tread. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains supple with no bolster wear, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car aroma. All electronic components, from the premium sound system to the advanced driver-assist features, operate with precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, backed by a meticulous service history performed exclusively at authorized dealerships. It has been climate-control garage-kept and never exposed to harsh weather or salt. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a vehicle that is indistinguishable from one on a dealer's showroom floor.",
      "price": 48500.0,
